#### [MODIFY] [auth/register/page.tsx](file:///home/jasurbek/Desktop/ozodbek/hotel/src/app/auth/register/page.tsx)
- Add a role toggle: two buttons "I'm a Customer" / "I'm a Hotel Owner"
