### 5. Booking Form with Availability Check

#### [MODIFY] [hotels/[slug]/book/page.tsx](file:///home/jasurbek/Desktop/ozodbek/hotel/src/app/hotels/[slug]/book/page.tsx)
- After date selection, call the availability API before submitting
